#X text 24 263 Description: This is an emulation of the TR-808 snare
drum made by comparing recordings of actual hardware at various knob
setting levels to reverse engineer the audio synthesis. This took about
2 days and I think it sounds pretty damn good. The control values match
the 808 controls except for the addition of the tuning (for hip-hop
tracks of course).;
